<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Yoga Plan</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="Css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar fixed-top navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Healthcare</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/home">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/yoga">Yoga</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <section class="gradient_background">
        <div class="yogacontain">
            <h2 class="py-5 fw-bold">Yoga Exercise Plan for <%=heading%> (BMI : <%=bmi%>)</h2>
            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <div class="yoga-card p-5">
                        <% if (bmi < 18.5) { %>
                            <h2 class="pt-2 pb-5 fw-bold">Underweight (BMI &lt; 18.5):</h2>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Start with gentle yoga poses to improve flexibility and mobility.</li>
                                <li>Incorporate breathing exercises (pranayama) to reduce stress and promote relaxation.</li>
                                <li>Focus on restorative yoga poses to relax the body and calm the mind.</li>
                                <li>Practice yoga sequences that target muscle strengthening and toning.</li>
                                <li>Consult with a certified yoga instructor to create a personalized yoga practice suited to your needs.</li>
                            </ul>
                        <% } else if (bmi >= 18.5 && bmi <= 24.9) { %>
                            <h2 class="pt-2 pb-5 fw-bold">Normal Weight (BMI 18.5 - 24.9):</h2>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Explore a variety of yoga styles such as Hatha, Vinyasa, or Iyengar to find what suits you best.</li>
                                <li>Practice yoga poses that focus on balance, flexibility, and strength to maintain overall well-being.</li>
                                <li>Incorporate breathing techniques and meditation to reduce stress and improve mental clarity.</li>
                                <li>Join yoga classes or workshops to deepen your practice and connect with a community.</li>
                                <li>Consistency is key – aim to practice yoga regularly to experience its full benefits.</li>
                            </ul>
                        <% } else if (bmi >= 25 && bmi <= 29.9) { %>
                            <h2 class="pt-2 pb-5 fw-bold">Overweight (BMI 25 - 29.9):</h2>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Choose yoga poses that focus on building strength and boosting metabolism, such as power yoga or hot yoga.</li>
                                <li>Incorporate dynamic yoga flows to increase heart rate and burn calories.</li>
                                <li>Practice yoga sequences that target core muscles to support weight loss and improve posture.</li>
                                <li>Combine yoga with other forms of exercise like cardio and strength training for optimal results.</li>
                                <li>Consult with a qualified yoga instructor or personal trainer to create a well-rounded fitness plan.</li>
                            </ul>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <h2 class="pt-2 pb-5 fw-bold">Obese (BMI ≥ 30):</h2>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Start with gentle yoga poses to improve flexibility and mobility without putting strain on joints.</li>
                                <li>Focus on yoga sequences that emphasize relaxation and stress reduction to support overall well-being.</li>
                                <li>Incorporate restorative yoga poses to promote relaxation and aid in recovery.</li>
                                <li>Practice yoga breathing techniques to reduce anxiety and promote mental clarity.</li>
                                <li>Gradually increase the intensity and duration of your yoga practice as your fitness level improves.</li>
                                <li>Consult with a qualified yoga instructor or healthcare professional to ensure a safe and effective yoga practice.</li>
                            </ul>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>

